{"tid":512141,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"各位賭輸錢／短炒輸錢嘅朋友們有福了，737幫到你回本！","createTime":"2017-12-28T07:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T06:39:36.000Z","uid":9506,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd70b889a8b4ca5dd9ad4472a7338d90cfe99bf","tid":512141,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"講明先，737呢隻唔係咩短炒股，適合想儲錢／有穩定增幅嘅朋友仔，上咗圖先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/152657_f9e0bc476433a5ec03ddaa24a2ec3bdf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F152657_f9e0bc476433a5ec03ddaa24a2ec3bdf.png&h=e808ff29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好明顯見到呢隻股基本上係唔會跌，近乎無敵，兼且佢宜家個價仲係5蚊，長hold上一蚊你都咪話唔發，仲要有息派<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一個好重要嘅原因係因為呢隻股所屬嘅板塊來年會造好，所以宜家買入都無咩問題。<br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟家姐有貨係手"},{"pid":"8ec9bc6e46c03cf7474a6139f29344a18d41e57f","tid":512141,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"btw，唔該個啲跟咗／覺得呢個post有用嘅巴打自動自覺畀正皮，始終挑選一隻股票需時甚長<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ada171726d4200284ca0df9ed270565e4a0945","tid":512141,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"推到畀出邊個位過大海輸錢巴打見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf48cc893cfe8df89fcf959d8cb693eeab40cc4","tid":512141,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"推咁多隻，買唔到咁多呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44922b13a2397d451e613b9b517d28d886d3e737","tid":512141,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7bf48cc893cfe8df89fcf959d8cb693e